    <item>
      <title>普京的央行行长加息激怒俄罗斯精英</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/russian-elite-is-angry-at-putin-s-central-banker-over-rate-hikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯央行行长纳比乌琳娜长期以来一直被誉为在乌克兰战争导致的制裁中拯救俄罗斯经济的“救星”，但她现在却日益受到官员的攻击，他们称她正在用创纪录的高利率摧毁俄罗斯经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/russian-elite-is-angry-at-putin-s-central-banker-over-rate-hikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 07:55:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国海军上将称特朗普上台后美国越南政策不太可能改变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/us-vietnam-policy-unlikely-to-change-with-trump-us-admiral-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国印度太平洋司令部司令在河内举行的简报会上表示，在即将上任的特朗普政府期间，美国很可能继续其当前的政策，让越南参与军事行动和活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/us-vietnam-policy-unlikely-to-change-with-trump-us-admiral-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 06:05:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>药物过量死亡人数减少，美国人预期寿命上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/us-life-expectancy-climbs-on-fewer-drug-overdose-deaths</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据新报告显示，由于药物过量死亡人数减少，美国的出生预期寿命升至新冠疫情爆发以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/us-life-expectancy-climbs-on-fewer-drug-overdose-deaths</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 05:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
